title: Help with a font I think I should know...
content:
This one has me really stumped. It’s one of those fonts that looks familiar, but the more I look for it, it might just be that it looks really close to other fonts. The closest I have come is Celeste from FontFont, but the t, d, b, etc is different. Does anyone recognize this one? Help, please.
